<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFC36A7CFF4E934F1B64BEB4" pageId="56" pageNumber="814" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFC36A7CFF4E934F1B64BEB4" blockId="56.[176,1383,828,1492]" pageId="56" pageNumber="814">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFFC36A7CFF4E934F1C11BE05" bold="true" box="[178,529,1302,1335]" pageId="56" pageNumber="814">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. Virtually nothing is known regarding ecology and threats of the Red-brown Pipistrelle; further studies are needed. Recorded from Mount Palung and Kayan Mentarang national parks.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
